General.Name: Pacte Novation
General.Description: Pacte Novation operates as a software engineering company, provides information systems, expert systems, embedded systems, and software publishing in France. The company offers business information system software, an organized set of resources making it possible to collect, store, process and distribute all the information flows; real-time embedded systems; artificial intelligence software; big data & data science; AxiomCAD Elec, an electrical schematic software; and artificial intelligence training on ODM themes. It also provides railways information systems, such as ERTMS systems; CBTC systems for automatic metros; control-command systems; interlocking systems, which include PAI, PIPC, and PMI; supervision comprising PCC and simulators; operational assistance consisting of optimization of lane inspection rounds, system passenger information, timetables, and fares; and provision of technical data management comprising execution studies, track/technical plans, catenary studies, etc. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Issy-les-Moulineaux, France.
General.Address: 2, rue du Docteur Lombard, Issy-les-Moulineaux, France, 92130
